"15"/></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="15"><CHAR>표준형을 행렬형태로 고치면 다음과 같다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="15"/></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="15"><EQUATION BaseLine="88" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2054688077" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="3"><SIZE Height="1175" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="4225" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>rm max`````c  ^{T} x</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="15"><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2054688078" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="4"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="5445" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>s.t````````` rm Ax=b</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="15"><CHAR>     </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="86" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2054688079" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="5"><SIZE Height="1000" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="2595" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>rm x GEQ 0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="15"/></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="1"><CHAR>단체법(simplex method)</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="15"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>o G.B Dantzig가 최초로 개발(1947)</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>o 선형계획의 최적해는 항상 실행 가능한 영역의 꼭지점에서 결정된다는 </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>  원리를 이용해 대수적 방법으로 해를 도출</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="15"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>표준형의 제약조건식은 m개의 방정식과 m+n개의 미지수가 있는 부정방정식(不定方程式) 으로서 이대로는 방정식을 풀 수 없다. 방정식의 수를 초과하는 변수들의 값을 미리 고정시켜야만 유일한 해 도출 가능</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>n개의 변수값을 0으로 지정하는 것이 가장 쉬운 방법인데, 그 경우의 수는 </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="67" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2056376946" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="23"><SIZE Height="2100" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="3355" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>LEFT ( pile{m+n#n} RIGHT )</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> 으로 결정변수의 수가 많으면 모든 경우를 다 고려하는 것은 불가능</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>심플렉스법은 처음에 n개의 의사결정변수를 0으로 지정하고 나머지 m개의 값을 구하는데, 이때 0으로 지정된 n개의 변수들을 비기저변수(非基底變數 ; non-basic variable), 나머지 m개의 변수를 기저변수(基底變數 ; basic variable)라 한다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>기저변수의 값들을 기저해(基底解 ; basic solution)라고 하고, 음수가 없는 기저해를 실행가능기저해(basic feasible solution), 음수가 있으면 실행불가능(infeasible), 기저해에 0이 있으면 퇴화(退化 ; degeneracy)된 해라고 한다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>심플렉스법은 m개의 여유변수를 초기 기저변수, n개의 의사결정변수를 초기 비기저변수로 시작하여, 비기저변수 중에서 목적함수값을 향상시킬 수 있는 변수를 새로운 기저변수로 삼는 과정을 반복하여, 목적함수가 더 이상 향상될 수 없을 때 최적해를 얻는 방법이다.</CHAR><FOOTNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="1" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="6"><AUTONUM Number="1" NumberType="Footnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> </CHAR><FIELDBEGIN Command="http\://grandguy.tistory.com/49;1;0;0;" Dirty="true" Editable="false" InstId="2054689411" Property="0" Type="Hyperlink"/></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="2"><CHAR>http://grandguy.tistory.com/49</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="6"><FIELDEND Editable="false" Property="0" Type="Hyperlink"/><CHAR> </CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></FOOTNOTE><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="15"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="1"><CHAR>단체법의 행렬 표현</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="15"/></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="15"><CHAR>x를 basic variables, non-basic variables로 구분, 행렬 A, 벡터 c도 이에 상응하게 분할</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="15"/></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="15"><EQUATION BaseLine="64" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2054688080" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="6"><SIZE Height="2504" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="13370" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>rm A=(B```D)`,`c= LEFT ( pile{c  _{B}#c  _{D}} RIGHT ) ,``x= LEFT ( pile{x  _{B}#x  _{D}} RIGHT )</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="15"/></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="15"><CHAR>표준형은 다음과 같이 바뀐다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="15"/></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="15"><EQUATION BaseLine="76" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2054688087" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="7"><SIZE Height="1365" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="10310" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>rm max`````z`=`c  _{B} ^{T} x  _{B} +`c  _{D} ^{T} x  _{D}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="15"><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2054688088" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="8"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="9175" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>s.t````````` rm Bx  _{B} +Dx  _{D} =b</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> ..............①</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="15"><CHAR>     </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2054688089" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="9"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="7490" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>rm x  _{B}  GEQ 0`,````x  _{D}  GEQ 0</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="15"/></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="15"><BOOKMARK Name="산업연관분석(Input/Output Analysis)"/><CHAR>①을 xB에 대해서 정리하면</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><EQUATION BaseLine="72" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2054688091" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="10"><SIZE Height="1190" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="6915" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>` rm Bx  _{B} =b-Dx  _{D}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>⇒</CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="76" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2054688093" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="11"><SIZE Height="1365" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="8938" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>` rm x  _{B} =B  ^{-1} (b-Dx  _{D} )</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>이를 목적식에 대입하면</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><EQUATION BaseLine="76" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2054688095" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="12"><SIZE Height="1365" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="7785" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>rm `z`=`c  _{B} ^{T} x  _{B} +`c  _{D} ^{T} x  _{D}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><EQUATION BaseLine="76" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2054688097" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="13"><SIZE Height="1365" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="15076" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>rm `z`=`c  _{B} ^{T} (B  ^{-1} b-B  ^{-1} Dx  _{D} )+`c  _{D} ^{T} x  _{D}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><EQUATION BaseLine="76" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2054688099" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="14"><SIZE Height="1365" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="14256" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>rm ``=`c  _{B} ^{T} B  ^{-1} b+(`c  _{D} ^{T} -c  _{B} ^{T} B  ^{-1} D)x  _{D}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="14" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><EQUATION BaseLine="76" BaseUnit="1000" LineMode="false" TextColor="0" Version="Equation Version 60"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2054688101" Lock="false" NumberingType="Equation" ZOrder="15"><SIZE Height="1365" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="6060" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Para" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="0" Left="56" Right="56" Top="0"/><SHAPECOMMENT>수식입니다.</SHAPECOMMENT></SHAPEOBJECT><SCRIPT>rm ``=`z  _{0} +`r  _{D} ^{T} x  _{D}</SCRIPT></EQUATION><CHAR> , </CHAR><EQUATION BaseLine="76" BaseUnit="1