neWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="13" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>0</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="2" ColAddr="5" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="282" Protect="false" RowAddr="4" RowSpan="1" Width="3812"><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="13" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>0</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="2" ColAddr="6" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="282" Protect="false" RowAddr="4" RowSpan="1" Width="3812"><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="13" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>0</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="2" ColAddr="7" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="282" Protect="false" RowAddr="4" RowSpan="1" Width="3812"><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="13" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>1</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="2" ColAddr="8" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="282" Protect="false" RowAddr="4" RowSpan="1" Width="3604"><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="13" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>0</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="2" ColAddr="9" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="282" Protect="false" RowAddr="4" RowSpan="1" Width="3604"><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="13" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P></PARALIST></CELL></ROW></TABLE><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>기준열(pivot column) 정하기</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>z 행에서 음의 값 중 절대값이 가장 큰 값을 찾음</CHAR><FOOTNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="1" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="6"><AUTONUM Number="2" NumberType="Footnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> 비기본변수 중 목적함수값을 가장 많이 증가시키는 변수를 진입변수로 선택하는 것임. x2의 z계수가 3이라는 것은 x2의 선택은 z가 3만큼 감소한다는 뜻이므로 선택하면 안됨.</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></FOOTNOTE><CHAR> </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>max{-|-2|,-|-1|} = -2 이므로 x1이 기준열</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>기준행(pivot row) 정하기</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>RHS 원소를 기준열인 x1 원소으로 나눈값(test ratio) 중 최소값을 기준행으로 정함</CHAR><FOOTNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="1" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="6"><AUTONUM Number="3" NumberType="Footnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> 진입변수 x1의 증가가 우변상수 제약조건을 침해해서는 안되므로 비율의 최소값을 퇴출변수로 선택</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></FOOTNOTE><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>(단 기준열 중 0 또는 음수는 제외) </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>min{10/1=10, 3/4, 10/2=5}=3/4 이므로 s2가 기준행</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>기준원소(pivot element) : 4 가 기준원소가 됨</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>기본변수가 s2에서 x1으로 바뀜. </CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>s2 퇴출변수(departing variable), x1 진입변수(entering variable)</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>축조작(pivoting)</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="3"><FOOTNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="1" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="6"><AUTONUM Number="4" NumberType="Footnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> 또는 행조작(row operation) 이라고 한다.</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></FOOTNOTE><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>기준원소를 1로 만듦.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>s2행/4</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>기준행외의 다른 요소를 0으로 만든다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>첫째 행 – 둘째 행</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>셋째 행  – 2 × 둘째 행</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>z 행  + 2 × 둘째 행</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>&lt;표2&gt; </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><TABLE BorderFill="2" CellSpacing="0" ColCount="10" PageBreak="Cell" RepeatHeader="true" RowCount="5"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2056376967" Lock="false" NumberingType="Table" ZOrder="27"><SIZE Height="6410" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="fa