IST></CELL></ROW></TABLE><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>기준열(pivot column) 정하기</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>여유변수가 음수인 행(s2, s3) 중에 첫 번째 행(s2)에서 가장 큰 양의 값을 찾음</CHAR><FOOTNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="15" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="6"><AUTONUM Number="5" NumberType="Footnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> 여유변수가 음수값을 갖는 것은 feasible 해가 아니므로(모든 변수는 양의 값을 가져야 함) 음의 여유변수를 가장 먼저 퇴출시키기 위함.</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></FOOTNOTE><CHAR> </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>max{4, 1} = 4 이므로 x1이 기준열</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>기준행(pivot row) 정하기</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>RHS 원소를 기준열인 x1 원소으로 나눈값(test ratio) 중 최소값을 기준행으로 정함</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>(단 기준열 중 0 또는 음수는 제외) </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>ratio 테스트에서 s2 선택</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>기본변수가 s2에서 x1으로 바뀜. </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>s2 퇴출변수(departing variable), x1 진입변수(entering variable)</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="0"><CHAR>축조작(pivoting)</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>기준원소를 1로 만듦.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>s2행/4</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>기준행외의 다른 요소를 0으로 만든다.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>첫째 행 – 둘째 행</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>셋째 행  – 2 × 둘째 행</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>z 행  + 2 × 둘째 행</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"/></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>&lt;표2&gt; </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="0" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><TABLE BorderFill="2" CellSpacing="0" ColCount="10" PageBreak="Cell" RepeatHeader="true" RowCount="5"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="2056479521" Lock="false" NumberingType="Table" ZOrder="33"><SIZE Height="6410" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="37987" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="10962" HorzRelTo="Paper" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="30572" VertRelTo="Paper"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="140" Left="140" Right="140" Top="140"/></SHAPEOBJECT><INSIDEMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="510" Right="510" Top="141"/><ROW><CELL BorderFill="2" ColAddr="0" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="282" Protect="false" RowAddr="0" RowSpan="1" Width="3812"><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="13" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="3"><CHAR>b.v</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="2" ColAddr="1" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="282" Protect="false" RowAddr="0" RowSpan="1" Width="3812"><PARALI